---
Disable an account without deleting local cached mail

Usage: mxr accounts disable [OPTIONS] <NAME>

Arguments:
  <NAME>

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format for `accounts` (the no-subcommand listing) [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
